query:
SELECT s.id, s.name, a.training_restrictions, a.muscle_emphasis, a.cardio_activities, a.main_goal, a.exercise_experience 
FROM students s 
LEFT JOIN student_anamnesis a ON s.id = a.student_id 
WHERE s.name LIKE '%Laura%' 
LIMIT 1;
